snippet.title: [MAME] Spider-Man - Black Cat and Doc Ock GameKey (c)2005 JAKKS Pacific
snippet.description: This shows the gameplay from the Black Cat and Doc Ock GameKey running in MAME.  It adds more levels in a similar style to the first game in the 5-in-1 but with a smoother framerate.  I'm not sure what the strats are for the boss.
